name: Wendy Marvel [Lora]
description:
This is a LORA for Wendy Marvel from Fairy Tail

I would recommend LORA weight 0.6-0.8

Would recommend to use Twintails and Blue hair for generating

This is my first try for LORA training I thought it was good and I wanted to share it with you guys.

NSFW should work I put some in training but never tried NSFW

Trained with Anything V3

If you enjoy this LORA, I genuinely love seeing your creations with it
